description:
Darkness Radio presents Supernatural News/Parashare: Shopping for Haunted Real Estate Edition with Mallie Fox!! 

It has been a week of buying, selling, and moving in the world of the paranormal and Tim and Mallie have unpacked all the boxes and sifted through the stories for you!

This week,  The Conjuring house has sold AGAIN... this time, for a record amount!  A haunted castle in Scotland DROPS it's price, AI wants to take over your bodies and crush your berries, and a bearded dragon fights SpongeBob, and LOSES!

Check out all things Mallie Fox here: https://www.paranormalgirl.com/

Get your tickets for the 2022 Michigan Paracon and come hang out with Tim and Mallie:  https://saultstemarie.com/events-calendar/michigan-paranormal-convention/
